A vintage 1970s data visualization aesthetic showing streams of colorful punch card-style ribbons flowing from a massive filing cabinet into a funnel-shaped mechanical apparatus, emerging as a single organized golden thread that winds into a neat spool. The scene is rendered in muted olive greens, burnt oranges, and mustard yellows typical of the era, with halftone dot patterns in the background. Old CRT monitors with green phosphor displays are stacked around the edges, showing cascading numbers. The entire composition has a retro-futuristic quality with rounded corners, wood grain textures, and chrome accents reminiscent of 1970s office equipment advertisements.
